# MESSAGING-APP
A blogging application where user can create blog and follow other user
### Prerequisites
```
(1) NodeJs
(2) MongoDb
(3) Express
```

### Documentation

[Read API documentation Here](https://documenter.getpostman.com/view/4094306/blooging-app/RVu4Gpoc)

### Live Link

[Click here to use API](https://pure-atoll-88608.herokuapp.com)

## API Paths

### (1) POST /login
```
username : String
password : String
```
### (2) POST /register

```
username: String
firstname: String
lastname: String
password: String
blogurl: String
```

### (3) POST /blogpost

```
title: String
content : String
```

### (4) GET /feed

```

```

### (5) PUT /follow/{username}

```
/follow/{String}
```

